2024-04-16
* Release v2.3.0
* New subplugin type for loading elements from different sources
* Add subplugins oermod_resource (mod_resource), oermod_folder (mod_folder)
* Datastructure in backend has changed due to new requirements
* New identifier for oer elements due to possibility of adding Moodle external objects
* Database tables updated, see upgrade.php for more information
* Pull service (public metadata) application profile changed (v2.0.0)
* Backwards compatibility to application profile v1.0.0 with accept header parameter
* Slightly optimized frontend card/list view
* Set subplugin type oeruploader and zipper to deprecated, will be removed in future release

